Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原睦月  水瓶座  B型血  身高155cm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座右銘是「向前衝！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛藤芽生  金牛座  A型血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不太喜歡這種名堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明喜歡的不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻森光香  在學生會擔任書記
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩羯座  A型血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的話語是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃  停下來停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重來一次  重來一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是  做宣傳的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  甚麼時候拍下來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是稻森光香  在學生會擔任書記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的話語是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡的話語是「朋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「朋友」…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  因為播放時發生了一些故障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來將重新播放新的校歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點…  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  請各位欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要像這樣一事無成就和大家分開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的是甚麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是這首比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  重新聽過之後覺得原來的也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還待在這裡好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還待在這裡真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  這麼胡來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美～～！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把學園祭辦下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和最最重要的伙伴們一起做點甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  把學園祭辦下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  此刻  做只有我們才能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被蜜柑教育了  真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請簽個名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請簽個名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  拜託了……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是白費工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改變學校卻無法實現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我想那並不是白費工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候一起堅守學生宿舍的伙伴們的名字和長相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都記得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  沒有人願意簽名  還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就認輸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別洩氣  別洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有洩氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以簽名嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距學園祭復活署名裁決日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有46小時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十話  『集結的伙伴們』
